I wouldn’t mind going to a circus as long as I’m not too close of contact to the clowns.... But I had a dream on a Thursday night that the next morning during trail day at school my group who’s on the purple trail will be meet with a clown holding a chain saw on the other side of the little hill we had to cross in order to finish of where we wanted our trail to end.....So I was freaking out and told everyone to back up and start running back to the entrance and call for help... but I wasn’t take it my eyes off the clown...If anything I was actually ready to square up... the clown was coming closer and I started backing away and picked up a really big stick just in case (didn’t know how it was going to be a match for a chainsaw but hey at least I got something.) It started running and I started running entering the field and I saw my principal and classmates just up the the play ground and told them to run. The clown was still chasing me as I looked behind me and I entered the school building and told the teachers to lock all of the doors everyone was scrambling locking any enter way Into the building...Then my dream stop there I woke up the next morning almost forgetting it was trail day and I was so anxious for the time of trail... I didn’t say anything bc I didn’t want to freak anyone out on the trail today especially the little kids... so when it was time to enter the trail I immediately picked up the same stick in my dream but the only thing missing was the clown... I thought it moved to a different location in the trail but I never encountered a clown... thankfully it’s my last year at school so I’m safe.... or at least I think I am.....

snippet.textDisplay: I also always had this weird dreams since I was young. Sometimes it was about good things but more of the times it's about an accident, people around me always told me that if I dreamed about something that I think will happened one of these days or in future (?) I should tell it to my mom so it won't happened especially if it is bad one. One of the creepiest thing that I dream is the way how I'll die and I'm not the only one who dreamed about this, me and my two bestfriends dreamed about this at the same time. My dream is about how I jumped in the school building in my favorite corner in my school in second floor, at exactly 3 a.m I woke up and had this feeling of opening my messenger only to see my two  bestfriend messages asking if I'm ok and I said yes but kinda confused at the same time. The afternoon that day at school (my classes is  in the afternoon btw) this two bestfriend of mine told that they dreamed about me, one dreamed of me also jumping in the building and the one dreamed of my funeral. Someone told me the meaning of this is I'll live longer which is  crazy since I'm in my dark place that time I'm fine now and still that memory is crazy.

snippet.textDisplay:
My mom told me about a dream she had about her friend. In the dream he got into a car accident and went through the windshield.
Two nights later she got a call about her friend. He was in an accident but he'd been wearing his seatbelt. Instead his airbag didn't go off and his head hit the steering wheel.

My mom and I also tend to get really bad migraines before family or family friends pass away.
